{"tid":752212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得唔夾 但佢好愛我","createTime":"2018-07-22T15:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T09:35:42.000Z","uid":107566,"like":2,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"072dab9e514d1be73cec84db786398e8cd8ad674","tid":752212,"uid":107566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"佢係真係100%全心全意對我 對我好<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得自己未必真係可以對住佢一世<br />\n<br />\n我覺得我地既世界觀 價值觀都唔同<br />\n<br />\n好難去決擇 我怕我講分手佢會崩潰<br />\n<br />\n但一齊左咁耐都好有感情 但唔夾就係唔夾<br />\n<br />\n我O1 之前無諗清楚就去追 只係單純想有個女朋友<br />\n<br />\n唉 好後悔 好對佢唔住 由有分手既念頭開始後就不停挖佢d缺點出黎<br />\n<br />\n有無人有類似經驗分享下"},{"pid":"8db9ea23bb7adabb2211da792cd2d701c9baad20","tid":752212,"uid":135307,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:14:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"2e3d602b370f44410d93db5512e933a3b909c37d","tid":752212,"uid":137706,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:16:32.000Z","msg":"未玩夠就未玩夠 揾乜撚野藉口"},{"pid":"a4e1d3d7cab4c0aa26c27601e1d37d370b091925","tid":752212,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"價值觀點唔同？"},{"pid":"e6105c6eefecbcd07ea302ca42dcf78e5f8e0428","tid":752212,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"唔夾就唔好拖住人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb0c446c9d8404381257376f17243a1b6af9fb0","tid":752212,"uid":157023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e1d3d7cab4c0aa26c27601e1d37d370b091925","tid":752212,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:18:50.000Z","msg":"價值觀點唔同？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T15:39:03.000Z","msg":"講多少少<br />\n<br />\n我都試過類似"},{"pid":"35ebc33ac324507ad8c5efdb560935950fb4b765","tid":752212,"uid":107566,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e3d602b370f44410d93db5512e933a3b909c37d","tid":752212,"uid":137706,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score